WEBVTT

00:04:29.443 --> 00:04:34.621
For example, he discouraged giving
the diagnosis to children who had seizures

00:04:34.621 --> 00:04:38.382
but now we know that epilepsy
is very common in autism.

00:04:38.382 --> 00:04:41.424
He once bragged that he had turned
nine out of 10 kids

00:04:41.424 --> 00:04:45.255
referred to his office as autistic
by other clinicians

00:04:45.255 --> 00:04:47.883
without giving them an autism diagnosis.

00:04:48.503 --> 00:04:50.944
Kanner was a smart guy,

00:04:50.944 --> 00:04:53.113
but a number of his theories
didn't pan out.

00:04:53.113 --> 00:04:56.888
He classified autism as a form
of infantile psychosis

00:04:56.888 --> 00:05:00.858
caused by cold and unaffectionate parents.